{"word":"Weakness-Power","slug":"weakness-power","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Weakness-Power</b> - <b>(A) HUMAN WEAKNESS</b><p/><b>(1) Manifested in All Men</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=11&verse=14'>Num 11:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=26&verse=40'>Mat 26:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=16&verse=12'>Joh 16:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=3&verse=2'>1Co 3:2</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Frailty, TRANSIENT<p/><b>(2) Renders Men Dependent upon God</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=20&verse=12'>2Ch 20:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=127&verse=1'>Psa 127:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=23'>Jer 10:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=3&verse=27'>Joh 3:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=15&verse=5'>Joh 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=3&verse=5'>2Co 3:5</a><p/><b>(B) HELPLESSNESS,</b> physical and spiritual of man<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=13&verse=11'>Luk 13:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=7'>Joh 5:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=44'>Joh 6:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=15&verse=5'>Joh 15:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=3&verse=2'>Act 3:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=5&verse=6'>Rom 5:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=7&verse=18'>Rom 7:18</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Human Limitations, LIMITATIONS, HUMAN<p/><b>(C) MAN'S EXTREMITY,</b> of weakness, becomes God's opportunity to help,<p/>examples of<p/><b>The Psalmist</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=116&verse=6'>Ps 116:6</a><p/><b>The Disciples in the Storm</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=38'>Mar 4:38</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=48'>Mar 6:48</a><p/><b>The Sick Woman</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=25'>Mar 5:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=26'>Mar 5:26</a><p/><b>The Father of the Demoniac</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=17'>Mar 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=18'>Mar 9:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=5&verse=7'>Joh 5:7</a><p/><b>The Disciples Facing a Hungry Multitude</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=9'>Joh 6:9</a><p/><b>Peter in Prison</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=12&verse=6'>Ac 12:6</a><p/><b>Paul and his Companions on the Sea</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=27&verse=20'>Ac 27:20</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Deliverance Sought, DELIVERANCE<p/><b>(D) POWERLESSNESS</b> of men, often due to sin and unbelief<p/>Israel could not stand before their enemies<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=26&verse=37'>Lev 26:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=28&verse=32'>Deu 28:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=7&verse=12'>Jos 7:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=21'>Jdg 1:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=2&verse=14'>Jdg 2:14</a><p/>A broken covenant stripped Samson of his strength<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=17'>Jud 16:17</a><p/>Apostasy produced a nation of cowards<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=24'>1Sa 17:24</a><p/>Babylon enervated by idolatry<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=30'>Jer 51:30</a><p/>Unbelief rendered the apostles helpless to contend with Satanic forces<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=18'>Mar 9:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=15&verse=5'>Joh 15:5</a><p/><b>(E) EFFEMINACY,</b> general references to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=19&verse=16'>Isa 19:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=50&verse=37'>Jer 50:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=30'>Jer 51:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=3&verse=13'>Nah 3:13</a><p/><b>(F) POWER SPIRITUAL,</b> general references to<p/><b>Gives Men Courage to Rebuke Sin</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=3&verse=8'>Mi 3:8</a><p/><b>Mightier than Physical Forces</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=4&verse=6'>Zec 4:6</a><p/><b>Jesus the Supreme Example of</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=14'>Lu 4:14</a><p/><b>Accompanies the Baptism of the Holy Spirit</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=8'>Act 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=2&verse=2'>Act 2:2</a><p/><b>Enables Men to Speak with Authority</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=33'>Act 4:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=6&verse=8'>Act 6:8</a><p/><b>Fills Life with Healing Influences</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=11'>Act 19:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=19&verse=12'>Act 19:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=2&verse=4'>1Co 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=3&verse=16'>Eph 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=52&chapter=1&verse=5'>1Th 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=7'>2Ti 1:7</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Holy Spirit, HOLY SPIRIT<p/><b>(G) STRENGTH,</b> moral and spiritual promised<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=40'>2Sa 22:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=28&verse=5'>Isa 28:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=28&verse=6'>Isa 28:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=40&verse=31'>Isa 40:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=41&verse=10'>Isa 41:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=11&verse=32'>Dan 11:32</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=3&verse=16'>Eph 3:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=51&chapter=1&verse=11'>Col 1:11</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Invincibility, BATTLE OF LIFE<p/><b>(H) STRENGTH IN WEAKNESS,</b> promised<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=8&verse=2'>Psa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=27'>1Co 1:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=9'>2Co 12:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=12&verse=10'>2Co 12:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=13&verse=4'>2Co 13:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=33'>Heb 11:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=34'>Heb 11:34</a><p/><b>(I) GOD OUR STRENGTH</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=2'>Exo 15:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=22&verse=33'>2Sa 22:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=28&verse=8'>Psa 28:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=46&verse=1'>Psa 46:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=73&verse=26'>Psa 73:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=81&verse=1'>Psa 81:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=84&verse=5'>Psa 84:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=21'>Psa 89:21</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Confidence in God, FAITH<p/><b>(J) CHRIST'S POWER</b><p/><b>Saving</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=63&verse=1'>Isa 63:1</a><p/><b>Pardoning</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=6'>Mt 9:6</a><p/><b>Infinite</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=28&verse=18'>Mt 28:18</a><p/><b>Over Nature</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=8&verse=25'>Lu 8:25</a><p/><b>Over his own Life</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=10&verse=18'>Joh 10:18</a><p/><b>Life-giving</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=17&verse=2'>Joh 17:2</a><p/><b>Wonder-working</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=10&verse=38'>Ac 10:38</a><p/><b>Demonstrated by his Resurrection</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=1&verse=4'>Rom 1:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=1&verse=3'>Heb 1:3</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Christ, Creator, CHRIST JESUS<p/>Christ's Touch, ASSOCIATION<p/><b>(K) POWER OF GOD</b><p/><b>(1) General References to</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=29&verse=12'>1Ch 29:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=8'>2Ch 25:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=26&verse=12'>Job 26:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=62&verse=11'>Psa 62:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=65&verse=6'>Psa 65:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=93&verse=4'>Psa 93:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=34&chapter=1&verse=3'>Nah 1:3</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=16&verse=25'>Rom 16:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=16&verse=27'>Rom 16:27</a><p/><b>--SEE</b> Divine Ability, POWER<p/><b>(2) Is Infinite</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=42&verse=2'>Job 42:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=115&verse=3'>Psa 115:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=135&verse=6'>Psa 135:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=43&verse=13'>Isa 43:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=35&chapter=3&verse=6'>Hab 3:6</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=19&verse=26'>Mat 19:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=14&verse=36'>Mar 14:36</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=37'>Luk 1:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=6'>Rev 19:6</a><p/><b>(3) Special References to Divine Ability</b><p/>Able to Deliver<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=3&verse=17'>Da 3:17</a><p/>-- to raise up children from stones<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=8'>Lu 3:8</a><p/>-- to fulfil promises<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=4&verse=21'>Ro 4:21</a><p/>-- to make grace abound<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=9&verse=8'>2Co 9:8</a><p/>-- to do exceeding abundantly<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=49&chapter=3&verse=20'>Eph 3:20</a><p/>-- to subdue all things<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=50&chapter=3&verse=21'>Php 3:21</a><p/>-- to guard the soul's treasures<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=55&chapter=1&verse=12'>2Ti 1:12</a><p/>-- to save to the uttermost<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=7&verse=25'>He 7:25</a><p/>-- to keep from falling<p/><a href='S:Jude'>Jude</a><p/><b>(4) Enables God to use Weak Instrumentalities</b> to accomplish Great<p/>Results<p/>A rod<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=2'>Ex 4:2</a><p/>A jaw-bone<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=15&verse=15'>Jud 15:15</a><p/>Five smooth stones<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=40'>1Sa 17:40</a><p/>A handful of meal and a little oil<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=12'>1Ki 17:12</a><p/>A cloud the size of a man's hand<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=44'>1Ki 18:44</a><p/>Small things<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=4&verse=10'>Zec 4:10</a><p/>The mustard seed<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=32'>Mt 13:32</a><p/>Five barley loaves<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=6&verse=9'>Joh 6:9</a><p/>God's Instrument Case<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=1&verse=27'>1Co 1:27-29</a><p/><b>(L) DIVINE POWER OVER NATURE</b><p/><b>(1) Exhibited by Christ,</b> general examples of<p/>In multiplying the loaves<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=20'>Mt 14:20</a><p/>-- walking on the sea<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=25'>Mt 14:25</a><p/>-- discovering the tribute money<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=17&verse=27'>Mt 17:27</a><p/>-- blighting the fig-tree<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=19'>Mt 21:19</a><p/>-- stilling the tempest<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=39'>Mr 4:39</a><p/>-- turning water into wine<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=2&verse=7'>Joh 2:7</a><p/><b>(2) The Sea Controlled</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=26&verse=10'>Job 26:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=38&verse=8'>Job 38:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=38&verse=11'>Job 38:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=33&verse=7'>Psa 33:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=104&verse=9'>Psa 104:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=8&verse=29'>Pro 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=5&verse=22'>Jer 5:22</a><p/><b>(3) The Tempest Stilled</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=65&verse=7'>Psa 65:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=89&verse=9'>Psa 89:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=107&verse=29'>Psa 107:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=32&chapter=1&verse=15'>Jon 1:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=26'>Mat 8:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=14&verse=32'>Mat 14:32</a><p/><b>(4) The Wind ruled</b><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=148&verse=8'>Psa 148:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=30&verse=4'>Pro 30:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=39'>Mar 4:39</a><p/><b>(5)</b> General References to the Control of the Elements<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=7&verse=4'>Gen 7:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=9&verse=33'>Exo 9:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=11&verse=17'>Deu 11:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=37&verse=6'>Job 37:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=148&verse=8'>Psa 148:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=10&verse=13'>Jer 10:13</a>"}]}